headline: CHASE PROPERTIES EXPANDS NATIONAL FOOTPRINT WITH ACQUISITION OF SOUTHWEST RETAIL PORTFOLIO
summary: Chase Properties is pleased to announce the acquisition of the Southwest Portfolio, a four-property retail portfolio totaling 514,983 square feet with locations in Texas and Arkansas. This strategic transaction marks Chase Properties' entry into both states, expanding the company's growing footprint into four new markets.
